data.Name: J. Rabbit
data.Bio: J. Rabbit hails from the Bronx, NY, where he lives and breathes music. He is deathly afraid of zombies, suffers from and delights in synesthesia, and wants to write a song that will make people see green. He specializes in dubstep and DNB with a lot of wobble, sub, rattle & fun! For the korean do go to J Rabbit Read more on Last.fm
